VIA EPIA Dual Processor Motherboard!

original

Spec:
VIA EPIA DP Specifications
Processor

- 2 VIA EDEN-N NanoBGA Processors
- VIA Padlock Security Suite
- PowerSaver 3.0: Extends battery life by dynamically reducing power consumption
Chipset

- VIA CN400 North Bridge
- VT8237R South Bridge
System Memory

- 2 DDR400/333/266 SO-DIMM socket
- Up to 2GB memory size
VGA

- Integrated S3 Graphics UniChrome™ Pro AGP Graphics with MPEG-2 decoding & MPEG-4 acceleration
Expansion Slots - 1 PCI
- 1 mini PCI
Onboard IDE - 1 UltraDMA 133/100/66 Connector
Onboard S-ATA - 2 Serial ATA Port Connectors
Onboard LAN - VIA VT6122 10/100/1000 Base-T Ethernet Controller (GbE LAN)
- VIA VT6103L 10/100 Base-T Ethernet PHY
- i82451GI/i82551QM 10/100/1000 Base-T Ethernet Controller option
Onboard Audio - VIA Vinyl Six-TRAC 6-channel AC’97 Audio
Back Panel I/O

- 1 VGA Port
- 2 USB 2.0 Ports
- 2 RJ-45 LAN Ports
Onboard I/O Connectors - 2 USB 2.0 Connectors and 2 USB headers
- RJ45 header
- AC’97 header
- 1 SM Bus Connector
- PS2 header (headless architecture for KB/MS)
- CPU FAN
- 2 Serial Port Connectors for 1 Com Port and 1 10-pin header for RS232
- ATX Power Connector
BIOS

- Award BIOS
- 2/4Mbit flash memory
System Monitoring & Management

- CPU voltage monitoring
- Wake-on-LAN, Keyboard-Power-on, Timer-Power-on
- System power management
- AC power failure recovery
Form Factor

- Mini-ITX (4/6 Layers)
- 17 cm x 17 cm

頗吸引人的,他的顯示卡也支援mpeg4 加速(除了邪惡的wmv),加個 4port sata 擴充卡也可以做小型的 file server...cool!!!!
